ISLAMABAD, Oct 7 (APP):Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif Friday congratulated the Pakistan women cricket team for its win against India in the T20 match of the Asia Cup.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “Consistency and hard work are ingredients for success. Congratulations to our women cricket team for beating the arch rivals in a T20 match today. Well played. Pakistan is proud of you.”
